Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell bash
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1100
Set Height 680
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms
Set Padding 18

Hide
Type 'npx() { shift; node /workspaces/cursor-rules/src/cli.js "$@"; }'
Enter
Type "cd ~/ccdemo && rm -f AGENTS.md && clear"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Show

Sleep 1s
Type "npx cursor-compose --agents"
Sleep 700ms
Enter
Sleep 2800ms
Enter
Sleep 1800ms
Type "head -16 AGENTS.md"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 3500ms
